{"tid":741864,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食評：太子醉江南","createTime":"2018-07-14T05:26:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T08:00:45.000Z","uid":181719,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c65335173231e6993dfb412ef491a66e410fe31e","tid":741864,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T05:26:06.000Z","msg":"喺香港要食上海咸肉唔難，但要抵食就好難，個幾月前去試食過老雪園，2舊水，只係食到咸肉絲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n回帶<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/669023/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/669023/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android[/url]<br />\n<br />\n今次就介紹返一間上海菜館，65蚊就食到大大塊仲要部位靚嘅咸肉炒年糕喇。睇相，色澤夠靚，雖然偏肥，但勝在夠大塊同入味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/132222_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F132222_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c4acbf10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咸肉同清炒年糕真係perfect match黎。呢度炒功亦相當唔錯，有鑊氣得黎唔算多油，非常滿足。<br />\n<br />\n其實淨係一碟年糕都夠食，不過為咗多樣野寫，又叫多碗京式水餃，係白菜豬肉餡黎。白菜本身味道冇乜個性，只靠豬肉少少調味，加上碗湯亦冇乜味，食落稍嫌淡口。不過餃皮夠薄，肉汁算多42蚊碗絕對係中上水準喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/132258_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F132258_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=33c49617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/132317_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F132317_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=452f1c3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環境就唔算好坐，一個人食幾乎一定要搭檯。今次去，杯茶仲有陣洗潔精味，食完想飲啖茶「浪」吓口都唔敢，扣咗啲分。中意食咸肉嘅朋友，絕對值得黎；但係中意食小籠包嘅話，建議搭遠幾個站，食美孚新上海 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80fb45c2aa6f78cb95b0d4d8c3eaa29fa589495d","tid":741864,"uid":49549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T05:30:43.000Z","msg":"屋企成日煮上海年糕食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766e965284eb052e21392c83e45c52f4ff36db0a","tid":741864,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80fb45c2aa6f78cb95b0d4d8c3eaa29fa589495d","tid":741864,"uid":49549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T05:30:43.000Z","msg":"屋企成日煮上海年糕食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T05:35:56.000Z","msg":"正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 通常會落咩餡架？會唔會食上海咸肉？喺邊度買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e5135193530df7b979c66a65e4d82220b61491","tid":741864,"uid":49549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"766e965284eb052e21392c83e45c52f4ff36db0a","tid":741864,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80fb45c2aa6f78cb95b0d4d8c3eaa29fa589495d","tid":741864,"uid":49549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T05:30:43.000Z","msg":"屋企成日煮上海年糕食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTim